test_justification: "go test" will test the project, as will "make test". We do not use any other testing suites, and Go is FLOSS
test_invocation_justification: "go test" is the standard way to invoke tests in golang, and we support that for all tests.
test_most_justification: Trickster has 70% code coverage and covers the only code branch (master) as well as any prospective pull request branches. See https://travis-ci.org/Comcast/trickster/jobs/491921371

warnings_strict_justification: TravisCI will fail any build that does not pass a lint test with a 100% score, including Pull Requests.
